dreisoft.tresos.generator.ng.api.cds.ctypes

Class Array<T extends CType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • dreisoft.tresos.generator.ng.api.cds.ctypes.CType
      • dreisoft.tresos.generator.ng.api.cds.ctypes.ComplexType
        • dreisoft.tresos.generator.ng.api.cds.ctypes.Array<T>

  • public final class Array<T extends CType>
extends ComplexType
    Represents an array of generic type T in the C language. This class is final because it's not possible to define types of arrays. To create multi-dimensional arrays an Array can consist of further arrays.

    Copyright (C) Elektrobit Automotive GmbH - All rights reserved

    2008.b
